{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Knock_on_the_door",
  "title": "The Knock on the Door",
  "summary": "Seeking discreet help, the black-clad operative Zeak Oppenhiemer tracks down the off-duty ambassador Ambrosia Aderanne at her secluded beachside home, where she is unwinding with her mother Raina and daughters Liora and Gabi. After shooing the family out of earshot and masking the room with music, Ambrosia learns that Agent Rendolen's botched sabotage has blown a covert mission to free enslaved Wookiees, forcing the Imperial Lord Thel to move the deal and hunt a leak. Zeak proposes shoring up his cover by having the Republic stage X-wing strikes against the innocent Trigdale Metalurgy mines as a smokescreen, and dangles a far larger prize: using Corellian Engineering Corporation influence and a seat on the CSA's Direx board to slowly outlaw slavery in the Corporate Sector. He also reveals a 40-billion-credit short-selling scheme against Trigdale to sow financial chaos and offers Ambrosia a chance to invest. Wary but intrigued, she promises to weigh the risks and protect her fragile family before committing, and the conversation ends when her terrified daughter Gabi interrupts and Zeak quietly takes his leave.",
